wsdl:operation.name: AddShipment
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: <doc><summary> Adds a shipment to Centiro system </summary> <param name="requestMessage"></param> <returns></returns><required>False</required></doc>

wsdl:operation.name: AddMasterShipment
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: <doc><summary> Adds a master shipment to centiro system </summary> <param name="requestMessage"></param> <returns></returns><required>False</required></doc>

wsdl:operation.name: CancelShipment
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: <doc><summary> Deletes a shipment from Centiro system </summary> <param name="requestMessage"></param> <returns></returns><required>False</required></doc>

wsdl:operation.name: DeleteParcel
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: <doc><summary> Cancel parcels on a shipment </summary> <param name="requestMessage"></param> <returns></returns><required>False</required></doc>

wsdl:operation.name: AddAndPrintParcels
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: <doc><summary> Adds the parcels to the specified shipment and returns the printed labels </summary> <param name="requestMessage"></param> <returns></returns><required>False</required></doc>

wsdl:operation.name: CloseShipments
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: <doc><summary> Runs end of day on the list of shipments </summary> <param name="requestMessage"></param> <returns></returns><required>False</required></doc>

wsdl:operation.name: CloseAndUpdateShipments
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: <doc><summary> Runs end of day on the list of shipments, updates parcels and orderlines information. </summary> <param name="requestMessage"></param> <returns></returns><required>False</required></doc>

wsdl:operation.name: PrintParcels
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: <doc><summary> Returns the printed labels for the requested parcels </summary> <param name="requestMessage"></param> <returns></returns><required>False</required></doc>
